<div class="section_title">Behind the Scenes</div>
<span class="text">
Check out <EM>Behind the Scenes at CES </EM>for updates on the extra efforts the International CES makes to create a positive show experience for you.
<P><STRONG><A href="#" name=scene1></A>On-site Navigation</STRONG><BR>We’re making it even easier for International CES attendees to navigate the show floor. This year,&nbsp;a new on-site navigation system&nbsp;incorporates product category icons and colors.</P>
<P>The International CES addresses many vertical markets and can be viewed as having various shows-within-a-show. Eight icon images will represent the eight primary product categories at the International CES; look for them on the show floor&nbsp;as you walk the halls.&nbsp;In addition to helping attendees understand what products are where, the icons will be used in conjunction with a hall <A href="/print/docs/CESProductLocatorIcons.pdf" target=_blank>color-coding system (pdf)</A>.&nbsp; </P>
<P>For example, the Central Hall’s icons, video and audio, will be on a blue sign, and the carpet will be blue. The North Hall’s mobile icon will be on a green sign, and the carpet will be green. </P>These navigation tools will be used extensively in our pre-show promotion and on-site signage and materials, making it easier for attendees to reach their destinations.
</span>
