<div class="section_title">Invite Your VIPs to Your Booth</div>
<span class="text">
Increase your booth traffic, and make sure your most important customers get a personal invitation <EM>from you </EM>to the 2005 International CES.
<P>Whether you send a standard show invitation or a personalized invite to visit your booth at the show, make sure your VIPs have this year’s International CES on their calendars. The <STRONG>International CES exhibitor invitations </STRONG>offer exhibitors’ guests the opportunity to register for absolutely free—allowing them access to International CES exhibits, keynotes and SuperSessions. If they decide to register on-site, they’ll still save $25 with this invitation from you.&nbsp; </P>
<P>The initial shipment of 100 standard 2005 International CES exhibitor invitations was mailed to all exhibitors at the end of September. <BR>&nbsp;<BR><STRONG><EM>NEW! <BR></EM></STRONG>Exhibitors can now order additional invitations online at <A href="http://cesinvites.hbp.com/" target=_blank>http://cesinvites.hbp.com/</A>.&nbsp;It’s easy! Order up to 10,000 standard invitations printed by CES, or order customized invitations with your company name and booth information on them.</P>
<P>You’ll also have the option of having your exhibitor invitations mailed to your office or mail house to include with your own customer mailings, or having your invitations mailed directly from the printing/mail shop where they are printed. If you choose this option, you will see additional pricing information online. </P>
<P>Plan ahead. The deadline for exhibitor invitation orders is <STRONG>November 19, 2004</STRONG>. Attendees can pre-register for the 2005 International CES for <EM>free </EM>until December 30, 2004, at 8 p.m. EST. Distribute your exhibitor invitations in time for your customers to pre-register by the deadline—and make travel plans! </P>
<P>Questions? For more details, visit <A href="http://cesinvites.hbp.com/" target=_blank>http://cesinvites.hbp.com/</A>, e-mail <A href="mailto:invitations@CE.org">invitations@CE.org</A>, or call Andrew Bradley at (703) 907-4312.</P><STRONG><EM>Bonus! Mailing Lists</EM></STRONG><BR>‘Want to expand your direct mail reach and invite more attendees to see you at CES? Consider International CES <A href="/print/exhibitors/promotions/mail.asp">attendee mailing lists</A>, available only to official International CES&nbsp;exhibitors. For more information, contact Wendy Hudak at (703) 907-7688 or <A href="mailto:byb@CEorg">byb@CEorg</A>.
</span>
