<div class="section_title">Join Us at the 2005 International CES New York Press Preview</div>
<span class="text">
Each year the International CES New York Press Preview brings exhibitors together with more than 150 high-profile industry press members at an exclusive pre-show event. Join us there, November 10, 2004, at the Time Warner Center in New York City.&nbsp; 
<P>All International CES exhibitors are invited to attend! This is your chance to network with more than 150 high-profile journalists. Innovations 2005 honorees will be publicly announced for the first time ever at this event. Be there,&nbsp;and join the members of the media who are eager to hear the news.</P>
<P>To RSVP, please contact Jamie Lilly at <A href="mailto:jlilly@CE.org">jlilly@CE.org</A>. </P>
<P>Consider event sponsorship! The event includes exhibitor-sponsored displays and suites and an exclusive reception at one of Manhattan’s newest hot spots, the Stone Rose Lounge. Plus, exhibitor sponsors are invited to an executive luncheon with CEA President and CEO Gary Shapiro. </P>
<P>Put your company’s name and brand front and center at this year’s event. Exhibitors are invited to purchase an exhibitor display in the Stone Rose Lounge and&nbsp; a suite at the luxurious Mandarin Hotel to demonstrate their products and network with the press. By purchasing an exhibitor display and suite at the all-new event, your company will be listed as an official event sponsor and be entitled to:</P>
<UL>
<LI>Exhibitor display and suite at venue (suites include a two-night stay) </LI>
<LI>Pre-event media invitation list and post-event verified attendee list </LI>
<LI>Company name and logo on press materials, reception napkins, event signage, invitations and press gifts (<EM>subject to deadlines</EM>) </LI>
<LI>Recognition on&nbsp;<A href="https://cms.ce.org/default.htm">CESweb.org</A> </LI>
<LI>Mention during the CES press conference </LI>
<LI>Opportunity to distribute company gifts </LI>
<LI>Description and logo in pre-CES press e-mails (subject to deadlines) </LI>
<LI>Pre-event executive luncheon invitation</LI></UL><BR>To purchase an exhibitor display and suite, please contact Wendy Hudak at <A href="mailto:whudak@CE.org">whudak@CE.org</A> or (770) 643-7144.
</span>
