<P>Update your company contact and product information in the consumer electronics industry’s year ‘round sourcebook: the <EM>Official International CES Directory</EM>. Attendees can search via company contact information, brands, product categories, exporting information and financial exchange information.</P>
<P>Update your directory listing, and cross it off your <EM>To Do</EM> list. It’s easy, so <A href="/print/exhibitors/resource_center/directory/default.asp">get started&nbsp;</A><EM><A href="/print/exhibitors/resource_center/directory/default.asp">now!</A>&nbsp; </EM></P>
<P>Plus, it’s free to <A href="/print/exhibitors/resource_center/directory/rd_eims_company_logo.asp">list your company logo online</A>&nbsp;(login required).</P>
<P>Hurry! Listings updated by November 1, 2004 will be included in the official print directory, distributed on-site. Other updates may be made to the <A href="/print/exhibitors/resource_center/directory/default.asp">online directory</A> up through the show. </P>Questions? Please contact us at <A href="mailto:CESdirectory@CE.org">CESdirectory@CE.org</A>.
